    "rationale": "All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors reviewed. Seven factors were formally assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing critical epistemic gaps in model form selection, input uncertainty characterisation, and experimental sample adequacy. The aggregate credibility profile does not meet the required threshold for a Class III VAD device. The package is accepted for submission as a complete credibility dossier documenting current gaps; device clearance is not supported pending resolution of identified deficiencies.",
